{
  "stem": "422.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Jews got their money in the bank.' And they start beating up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they beat up my father so badly that our neighbor had a corset store on the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she saw my father laying in the gutter, bleeding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they meant to-- to-- to call a street-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --car with a-- with a horse, you know, those cars.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they put him on that car, and they brought him home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had to call our doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was a week in bed, very, very, very beaten up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Blue, all blue.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Those kind of things I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was in 1938, a war-- a year before the war broke out, not from the Germans, but from the Poles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The reaction was that my mother was writing letters to her brother, which was living here in-- in-- in New York, and begging him to do something, to strain himself to do.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever it's going to cost, we'll be able to work and pay back, to bring us over, to-- to do the legalities, do the papers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to bring us over to America.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That she got four nice kids, but they have no future.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She got-- there will be no future for them in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course, the brother, especially his wife, they didn't pay so much attention to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They told her-- the answer was, their letters was that it's very hard in America to find a job and to find an apartment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if your husband makes a living over there, so you better sit over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was the answer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That they didn't realize that it's that bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They thought that maybe my mother exaggerates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, it was not for a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
